text: Edita Kubelskienė (born 1 March 1974) is a former track and road cyclist from Lithuania. She represented her nation on the track at 2002, 2003 and 2004 and on the road at the 2004 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1974 births Category:Lithuanian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
